secubox-backup (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Full API: status, list, containers, create, restore, cleanup
  * Container backup/restore with automatic stop/start
  * Config backup: /etc/secubox, nginx, wireguard, haproxy, nftables
  * Services backup: /var/lib/secubox, nextcloud, gitea data
  * Modern dark-themed frontend with stats and history tables
  * Quick actions for full, config-only, containers-only backups

